WEBVTT

00:02.416 --> 00:04.952
...Did you check out the
theme for the dance?

00:05.670 --> 00:07.304
"Starry, Starry Night."

00:07.630 --> 00:08.899
Lame or what?

00:08.923 --> 00:10.641
Definitely the lamest.

00:11.968 --> 00:14.520
Oh, my God, I forgot
it was the yearbook.

00:14.554 --> 00:16.397
You like this color?

00:16.556 --> 00:17.857
I've got an idea.

00:19.183 --> 00:21.578
Excuse me. Is anyone in here?

00:21.602 --> 00:24.071
Um, I have an emergency.

00:26.148 --> 00:27.616
It's a girl thing.

00:33.072 --> 00:34.540
What's that little disk thing?

00:35.616 --> 00:36.677
I don't know.

00:36.701 --> 00:38.262
Maybe a deodorizer or something?

00:38.286 --> 00:39.513
Hmm.

00:39.537 --> 00:41.714
You think they're supposed
to hit it or avoid it?

00:41.831 --> 00:44.466
Beats me.

00:45.501 --> 00:46.886
So, what am I going to wear?

00:47.003 --> 00:48.220
To what?

00:48.713 --> 00:50.857
Hello, the dance.

00:50.881 --> 00:53.225
You just said how lame
it was going to be.

00:53.884 --> 00:55.237
Yeah, well,

00:55.261 --> 00:57.313
Michael Cassutt
kind of begged me.

00:58.264 --> 00:59.690
You're not going to go?

00:59.891 --> 01:02.202
No. No one asked me.

01:02.226 --> 01:03.944
Well, you're probably lucky.

01:04.477 --> 01:06.238
I don't think I'm
gonna stay very long.

01:06.355 --> 01:07.916
Oh, this is so gross.

01:07.940 --> 01:11.003
"Girls with the best legs.
Best butts."

01:11.027 --> 01:12.588
Oh, you're kidding.

01:12.612 --> 01:14.256
Look, you're here.

01:14.280 --> 01:16.300
"Girls we most want
to sleep with."

01:16.324 --> 01:17.384
Number two.

01:17.408 --> 01:18.792
Excuse me?

01:19.577 --> 01:21.013
Who's number one?

01:21.037 --> 01:22.880
Regina Lester.

01:22.914 --> 01:25.174
Oh, figures. Slut.

01:26.125 --> 01:27.301
Where are you?

01:27.668 --> 01:29.637
I'm not on it.

01:29.670 --> 01:31.555
Well, you've got to
be here somewhere.

01:31.672 --> 01:34.026
I'm not. Let's go.

01:34.050 --> 01:35.392
Oh, there you are!

01:35.551 --> 01:36.685
Where?

01:38.095 --> 01:40.314
"Girls we most want
to cheat off of."

01:42.933 --> 01:44.360
Guys are stupid.

01:46.000 --> 01:52.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

01:56.280 --> 01:57.998
- Trash cans?
- They're full.

01:58.574 --> 02:00.084
Put it outside.

02:01.160 --> 02:04.255
Just what I want to do right now.
Housework.

02:04.372 --> 02:06.215
Why did you have to
say yes, Charlie?

02:06.540 --> 02:08.175
What was I supposed to say?

02:08.584 --> 02:09.978
One of Mom and Dad's
best friends.

02:10.002 --> 02:11.939
She hasn't seen us
in three years.

02:11.963 --> 02:13.440
She wanted to check in.

02:13.464 --> 02:15.975
Great, exactly what
I'm in the mood for.

02:16.217 --> 02:17.434
A house-guest.

02:17.551 --> 02:19.186
Where is she gonna sleep?

02:20.304 --> 02:21.365
- Charlie's room.
- Charlie's room.

02:21.389 --> 02:23.033
Fine. I'll sleep on the couch.

02:23.057 --> 02:25.067
Serves you right after what
happened with Kirsten.

02:25.601 --> 02:28.205
Hey, I'm interviewing a nanny
today, okay, so lay off.

02:28.229 --> 02:31.282
Jeez, why is
everybody so crabby?

02:31.399 --> 02:32.376
Kirsten.

02:32.400 --> 02:33.575
Kate.

02:35.695 --> 02:37.121
Mind your own business.

02:38.280 --> 02:39.790
Greer...

02:40.366 --> 02:42.793
I can't really remember
what she looked like.

02:43.035 --> 02:44.461
She's kind of pretty.

02:45.079 --> 02:47.724
She was the one who sent that
gigantic wreath after the funeral.

02:47.748 --> 02:49.476
The one with the dried
fruits of the world on it.

02:49.500 --> 02:51.770
Yeah, the one we had to saw in half
to get through the front door.

02:51.794 --> 02:54.513
She babysat me once and let
me dye my hair burgundy.

02:55.548 --> 02:57.016
She sounds like fun.

02:57.508 --> 03:00.320
Yeah, just what we're
in the mood for...

03:00.344 --> 03:01.520
- Fun.
- Fun.

