<i>♪ Everybody wants to live ♪</i>

03:10.730 --> 03:12.457
<i>♪ Like they wanna live ♪</i>

03:12.481 --> 03:15.743
<i>♪ And everybody wants to love ♪</i>

03:15.776 --> 03:17.462
<i>♪ Like they wanna love ♪</i>

03:17.486 --> 03:20.706
<i>♪ And everybody wants to be ♪</i>

03:21.073 --> 03:25.711
<i>♪ Closer to free Everybody
